{"manifest_version":1,"info":{"id":"votsz_backup","name":"votsz's Backup","author":"votsz","version":"v2026_4_2","changelog":"CHANGELOG DETAILED 🇺🇸\n\n■ By holding a message in direct you can view without the person knowing that you have seen it (for now)\n\n■ Instagram for tablet in settings\n\n■ Possibility to add a separate caption for each post in a carousel (⛔️ not currently functional)\n\n■ Put banners on the profile of content you like to watch/interest in\n\n■ A quick button to add/move banners from your profile.\n\n■ The lives you do will be saved in your archives.\n\n■ New gender options for those who identify as another gender in the profile tab.\n\n■ It is now possible when editing a stories through the gallery, you drag up to change the photo.\n\n■ The blurred background in the stories is back.\n\n■ Notifications tab has had some changes.\n\n■ New look in the feed and reels related to people you follow and like.\n\n■ I put back the camera in the direct conversations because the gallery started to bug. "},"backup":{"104357:":["1: : true"],"70831:":["15: : true","12: : true","13: : true","17: : true","11: : true","10: : true","8: : true"],"64040:":["0: : true","2: : true"],"109190:":["0: : true"],"85663:":["2: : true","0: : true","1: : true"],"95315:":["1: : true","0: : true","2: : 1"],"69718:":["2: : true"],"91296:":["3: : true","2: : true","1: : true"],"83974:":["0: : true","1: : false"],"102290:":["1: : false","0: : false"],"87981:":["4: : true","2: : true","0: : true","6: : true"],"73763:":["18: : true","0: : true","13: : true","17: : false","3: : true","2: : true","1: : true","12: : true","5: : true","4: : true","14: : true","8: : true","16: : true","15: : true"],"78894:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"88691:":["3: : true","2: : true","1: : true"],"99473:":["1: : true"],"103969:":["0: : true"],"65438:":["1: : ADD_TO_YOUR_STORY,WHATSAPP_STATUS,CLIPS_DOWNLOAD,COPY_LINK,SYSTEM_SHARE_SHEET,WHATSAPP,LINE,KAKAOTALK,FACEBOOK,TWITTER,BARCELONA,USER_SMS,MESSENGER